                 BomberDove is a fun and addicting shooting 
                         game with a comic touch! Have you ever been 
                      bombed by a dove? Now's your chance to get 
                your revenge.
               Shoot the doves to score points, unlock 
             archivements and compare your score online 
              with OpenFeint. Play Timed mode to score as 
                     many points as you can within the time limit, 
               Endless mode for maximum score and Dodge mode 
         to see how long you can last without dying.

                your iDevice.
